# Annoscr is a noarch GJS application: the payload is interpreted JavaScript with
# no ELF objects, so RPM's automatic dependency generator finds no library
# sonames. The libadwaita and libportal runtime libraries — loaded at runtime via
# GObject-Introspection — must therefore be declared as explicit package
# dependencies. Filter rpmlint's explicit-lib-dependency advisory, which assumes
# such dependencies would be generated automatically.
addFilter(r"explicit-lib-dependency (libadwaita|libportal)")
